{"tid":943243,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)監獄瘋球 叛諜狂花 再造戰士1-3","createTime":"2018-12-16T11:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T18:58:24.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93825460f9952646a3c4085407a722eb0d4d9ed4","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d61b3ae0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=40247779\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2d1f6ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/40/TheLongestYard_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F40%2FTheLongestYard_poster.jpg&h=f7f12981&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/52/Salt_film_theatrical_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F52%2FSalt_film_theatrical_poster.jpg&h=5a9ac179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/93/Universal_soldier_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F93%2FUniversal_soldier_ver1.jpg&h=dde010a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.告保羅（阿當桑迪拿飾演）曾經是紅極一時的美式職業足球隊四分衛，卻因一次醉酒闖禍被關進監獄，聲名狼藉。獄長酷愛美式足球，卻生性殘忍。在獄長的特別要求下，告保羅被要求組織一支由囚犯組成的美式足球隊，挑戰手法兇狠的獄警隊。可是犯人們根本不是對手，備受壓力的告保羅，設法駕馭這些毫無紀律可言的囚犯。他在獄中遇上美式足球傳奇金牌教練尼特（畢雷諾士飾演）和另一囚犯包搞掂(基斯洛克飾演），兩人聯手團結囚犯共同對抗獄長，誓要將獄長打個遍甲不留..<br />\n<br />\n2.劇情描述美國中情局特務探員「伊芙&middot;莎特」（安潔莉娜&middot;裘莉飾）實際上是自小由前蘇聯在冷戰時期，以地獄式訓練，培養出來的臥底刺客，本名「娜塔莎&middot;宣科夫」。宣科夫在青少年時期取代了原本的莎特，利用莎特的美國公民身分長年潛伏在CIA，為的是籌劃已久的毀滅美國華府的「DAY X」。然而，在潛伏期間，她遇見了深情又顧家的昆蟲學者丈夫，潛伏前所受的特務的訓練開始失效<br />\n<br />\n3.越戰後，美國政府進行了一項絕密的科學計劃。科學家們將越戰中犧牲的士兵的屍體冰凍起來，植入電腦晶片，輸入戰爭程序，將他們改造成為新一代的戰爭機器人――「再造戰士」，這些機器人沒有情感和以前的記憶，只有冰冷的殺戮武器。士兵盧克（尚格&middot;雲頓 Jean-Claude Van Damme 飾）和班長安德魯（杜夫&middot;朗格 Dolph Lundgren 飾）就是其中兩員，他們被派往參加一場新的戰爭。戰爭中，兩人的晶片突然出錯.....<br />\n<br />\n4.尚克勞德範達美重返&ldquo;魔鬼命令&rdquo;戰場，再度披掛上場演出的生平第一部續集，當年人類異想天開的創造出宇宙戰士，到最後卻集體叛變。毫無人性、感情的宇宙士中，魯克（尚克勞範達美飾演）是一個改造失敗的例子，因為他殘存的人性，使得他在第一集裡，拯救了人類。<br />\n這次，魯克憑著他的經驗，成為改造宇宙戰士計劃的最佳指導。在魯克的監督之下，第二代的宇宙戰士設備更新穎、功能更強大。一旦他們失去控制，情況將無法收拾。不料，瑕疵再度出現，新一代的宇宙戰士，再度失控，危害人類的存亡。於是魯克再度出擊，務必確保人類的生存...<br />\n<br />\n5.20世紀60年代，美國的勢力向亞洲滲透，為此政府實行的一項絕密計劃&mdash;&mdash;戰士再造計劃，通過藥物注射等手段將士兵大造成冷血無情、實力強悍的超級戰士。隨著技術不斷改進，在羅伯特&middot;柯林博士的主持下又開啟了白塔計劃，成功打造出更為完美的第二代超級戰士。然而一次意外後12名二代戰士逃亡，而涉嫌叛國的柯林博士也被驅逐東歐。此後不久，再造戰士佔領切爾諾貝利，美國軍方決定派出4名尚存的一代戰士前...<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=33ca77ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=85f30d51\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a>裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b687dc8201b7cd839ca5302fba11df690cf17cb6","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c05ce92ccf56bd1fce1b778abf2aabfe3cc780","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bfd7b15a9a047db9e9870ac937da2a512db61c","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e008e63ef5872f4bf35ffd02cec238178e36831a","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3cc5a9611389a694df109bbdd6e02319da26a8","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T18:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9412fcee7a8ec0107affcd4c75221ab031b78b51","tid":943243,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T18:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}